        "detail": "You had agent coordination issues in 4+ sessions — zombie agents, lost context, stuck reviewers, and agents that couldn't relay outputs. For tasks under ~500 lines of changes, a single-agent approach with structured review steps is more reliable than spawning PM/Dev/Reviewer sub-agents. Reserve full team ceremony for large features only.",
